{"name": "easygems", "metadata": {"name": "easygems", "version": "0.0.14", "classifiers": ["Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13"], "home_page": "https://easy.gems.dkrz.de", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["cartopy", "cf_xarray", "healpix", "matplotlib", "numpy", "scipy", "xarray"], "summary": "Processing tools around km-scale earth system modeling", "upload_time": 1733174525}, "documentation": ["# easygems python package\n\n## install\n\nThe latest released version can be installed using:\n\n```\npip install easygems\n```\n\n## developing\n\nThis project uses [ruff](https://github.com/astral-sh/ruff) for code formatting and [pre-commit](https://pre-commit.com/) to run the formatter automatically.\n\nPlease ensure that you have `pre-commit` configured locally by running:\n\n```\npre-commit install\n```\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "easygems.remap", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "easygems.remap.compute_weights_delaunay", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "points", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "xi", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Compute remapping weights for linear interpolation.\n\nThe inerpolation is based on an internally computed Delaunay triangulation.\n\nArgs:\n    points (tuple[ndarrays]): Tuple with source grid coordinates.\n    xi (tuple[ndarrays]): Tuple with target grid coordinates.\n\nReturns:\n    xr.Dataset: Remapping information\n        \"src_idx\": Array with source grid indices\n        \"weights\": Remapping weights\n        \"valid\": Boolean mask determining if a target point is within the\n            triangulation. If it's outside, the target point will not\n            receive any data after interpolation any user might want\n            to set it to some missing value.\n\nSee also:\n    `apply_weights`"]}, {"name": "easygems.remap.apply_weights", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "var", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "src_idx", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "weights", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "valid", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Apply given remapping weights.\n\nArgs:\n    var (ndarray): Array to remap.\n    kwargs: Remapping weights as returned by `compute_weights`.\n\nReturns:\n    ndarray: Remapped values\n\nSee also:\n    `compute_weights`"]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "easygems.healpix", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "easygems.healpix.get_nest", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "dx", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easygems.healpix.get_nside", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "dx", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easygems.healpix.get_npix", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "dx", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easygems.healpix.get_extent_mask", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "dx", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "extent", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easygems.healpix.get_full_chunks", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "indices", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "chunksize", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Return indices of complete chunks, given a list of indices and a chunksize."]}, {"name": "easygems.healpix.isel_extent", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "dx", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "extent", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "easygems.healpix.broadcast_array", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "dx", "type": null, "def